  "questions": [
    {
      "text": "A 62-year-old man with a 40 pack-year smoking history presents to the ED with worsening dyspnea and wheezing over 3 days. He reports increased sputum production that is thick and yellow. Vital signs show a temperature of 37.7°C (99.9°F), HR 105, BP 160/95, RR 24, SpO2 90% on room air. Physical exam reveals bilateral expiratory wheezing, pursed-lip breathing, and use of accessory muscles. Jugular venous distention is present, and there are bilateral crackles at the lung bases with peripheral edema. CXR shows hyperinflated lungs with increased vascular markings and bilateral lower lobe infiltrates. What is the most appropriate initial treatment approach?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Albuterol, ipratropium, and systemic corticosteroids/p&gt;"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Furosemide and nitroglycerin with respiratory support"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Bronchodilators, corticosteroids, and furosemide"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Noninvasive positive pressure ventilation alone"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "Antibiotics and inhaled corticosteroids and beta-agonist therapy"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>This approach treats <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">AECOPD</a> but ignores the clear signs of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=fM0kLg&anker=Z8691613a1023ed6b2f562d848b9043be\" data-learningcard-id=\"fM0kLg\" data-anker=\"Z8691613a1023ed6b2f562d848b9043be\" data-section-id=\"3gcSEb0\">volume overload</a> including <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rS0faf&anker=Zfa99fa6ac238739f5e92fd88069c4036\" data-learningcard-id=\"rS0faf\" data-anker=\"Zfa99fa6ac238739f5e92fd88069c4036\" data-section-id=\"d-0owi\" data-sememe-id=\"S0by2H\">JVD</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=SM0yLg&anker=Z0df4decd39ceef9f9273076a08f8420e\" data-learningcard-id=\"SM0yLg\" data-anker=\"Z0df4decd39ceef9f9273076a08f8420e\" data-sememe-id=\"tZVXWG0\">peripheral edema</a>, and bilateral <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Z663ed2d3cd3880ca59f2d48341661e66\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Z663ed2d3cd3880ca59f2d48341661e66\" data-section-id=\"8CXOFZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"vQbABt\">crackles</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>This treats <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rS0faf&anker=Z07d22fa4c3f9da63ddf39683e4eaa845\" data-learningcard-id=\"rS0faf\" data-anker=\"Z07d22fa4c3f9da63ddf39683e4eaa845\" data-sememe-id=\"ak0QmT\">heart failure</a> with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Us0b8h&anker=Z7c92756b9ce2ff6d0c945d6ed0e082c2\" data-learningcard-id=\"Us0b8h\" data-anker=\"Z7c92756b9ce2ff6d0c945d6ed0e082c2\" data-sememe-id=\"vE0Ax3\">pulmonary edema</a> but ignores the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=qh0CUf&anker=Zfdfb82d83e675513c49619bc646fd20c\" data-learningcard-id=\"qh0CUf\" data-anker=\"Zfdfb82d83e675513c49619bc646fd20c\" data-section-id=\"PFcWRV0\" data-sememe-id=\"vIYAeq\">purulent</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Z893a8c8ecb23b11a8df0179f03b62956\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Z893a8c8ecb23b11a8df0179f03b62956\" data-section-id=\"sCXttZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"oaY0ln\">sputum</a>, smoking history, and hyperinflated <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ap0QLS&anker=Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-anker=\"Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\">lungs</a> suggesting an intercurrent pathology.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) CORRECT:</h4>Correct – The clinical presentation suggests both <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">AECOPD</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Aq0Rah&anker=Z3a0c593488fe90707a6fd3be1e3f2bdc\" data-learningcard-id=\"Aq0Rah\" data-anker=\"Z3a0c593488fe90707a6fd3be1e3f2bdc\" data-sememe-id=\"tO1X8S0\">acute heart failure</a>. The thick, yellow <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Z893a8c8ecb23b11a8df0179f03b62956\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Z893a8c8ecb23b11a8df0179f03b62956\" data-section-id=\"sCXttZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"oaY0ln\">sputum</a>, smoking history, and hyperinflated <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ap0QLS&anker=Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-anker=\"Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\">lungs</a> indicate <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">COPD exacerbation</a> requiring <span data-sememe-id=\"k4bmjF\">bronchodilators</span> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-section-id=\"Pq1WA30\" data-sememe-id=\"8AbOlw\">corticosteroids</a>; <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">antibiotics</a> could also be considered depending on markers of infection. The <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rS0faf&anker=Zfa99fa6ac238739f5e92fd88069c4036\" data-learningcard-id=\"rS0faf\" data-anker=\"Zfa99fa6ac238739f5e92fd88069c4036\" data-section-id=\"d-0owi\" data-sememe-id=\"S0by2H\">JVD</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=SM0yLg&anker=Z0df4decd39ceef9f9273076a08f8420e\" data-learningcard-id=\"SM0yLg\" data-anker=\"Z0df4decd39ceef9f9273076a08f8420e\" data-sememe-id=\"tZVXWG0\">peripheral edema</a>, bilateral <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Z663ed2d3cd3880ca59f2d48341661e66\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Z663ed2d3cd3880ca59f2d48341661e66\" data-section-id=\"8CXOFZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"vQbABt\">crackles</a>, and increased vascular markings indicate concurrent <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rS0faf&anker=Z07d22fa4c3f9da63ddf39683e4eaa845\" data-learningcard-id=\"rS0faf\" data-anker=\"Z07d22fa4c3f9da63ddf39683e4eaa845\" data-sememe-id=\"ak0QmT\">heart failure</a> requiring <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=gm0FUg&anker=Z5ad3a82094040255a4ea79209e2840c7\" data-learningcard-id=\"gm0FUg\" data-anker=\"Z5ad3a82094040255a4ea79209e2840c7\" data-sememe-id=\"3L0Sxg\">diuretic</a> therapy.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xq0E0h&anker=Z39ec6b94dcd469c1552ec36375de3926\" data-learningcard-id=\"xq0E0h\" data-anker=\"Z39ec6b94dcd469c1552ec36375de3926\" data-section-id=\"og10wT0\" data-sememe-id=\"YKcnUW0\">NIPPV</a> provides <span data-sememe-id=\"rZdf1o0\">respiratory support</span> but does not address the underlying pathophysiology.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>While this combination would effectively manage an infectious exacerbation of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3h0Sdf&anker=Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-learningcard-id=\"3h0Sdf\" data-anker=\"Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-sememe-id=\"Lk0woT\">COPD</a>, this approach misses the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rS0faf&anker=Z07d22fa4c3f9da63ddf39683e4eaa845\" data-learningcard-id=\"rS0faf\" data-anker=\"Z07d22fa4c3f9da63ddf39683e4eaa845\" data-sememe-id=\"ak0QmT\">heart failure</a> component.</div>",
